item.description: Would you please come and join us and bring some non-perishable food to a fun night at Studio Four in Pocasset. We will be having a great yoga class to raise money or food for the Pocasset Food Bank which is right out behind Studio Four. Have some fun, get some exercise, de-stress and help others! Entry is either food (peanut butter, pasta, stuffing, canned goods, sealed plastic drinks, rice, tuna, etc) or a cash donation.
item.name: Benefit Yoga Class for Pocasset Food Bank, held in Pocasset MA
